#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:1
msgid "使用交易策略"
msgstr "Uso de estrategias comerciales"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:3
msgid ""
"在 qteasy 中，交易策略（Strategy）负责在每一个运行周期内根据历史数据生成交易信号；Operator "
"是策略的容器与调度器，负责按既定频率与时间点运行策略并汇总信号；多个策略可归为 Group，同一 Group 内可通过 blender 表达式混合信号。"
msgstr ""
"En qteasy, una estrategia comercial (``Strategy``) generates trading signals"
" from historical data at each run step; ``Operator`` is the container and "
"scheduler that runs strategies at configured frequencies and times and "
"aggregates signals; multiple strategies form a ``Group``, and signals within"
" the same Group can be blended via a ``blender`` expresión."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:5
msgid "总体介绍"
msgstr "Descripción general"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:7
msgid ""
"**Strategy**：根据 DataType 获取的数据和可调参数，在 ``realize()`` 中计算并返回信号（如目标仓位、选股列表等）。"
msgstr ""
"**Estrategia**: utiliza datos de ``DataType`` and tunable parameters to "
"compute and return signals in ``realize()`` (por ejemplo, posiciones "
"objetivo o listas de selección de acciones)."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:8
msgid ""
"**Operator**：持有若干 Strategy，配置 "
"``signal_type``（PT/PS/VS）、``run_freq``、``run_timing``，在回测或实盘时按时间步调用策略并产出统一格式的信号。"
msgstr ""
"**Operator**: contiene uno o más ``Strategy`` instances, configures "
"``signal_type`` (PT/PS/VS), ``run_freq``, and ``run_timing`` e invoca "
"estrategias paso a paso en backtest o comercio en vivo para producir señales"
" en un formato unificado."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:9
msgid ""
"**Group**：相同 ``run_freq`` 与 ``run_timing`` 的策略会被归入同一 Group；每个 Group 可配置 "
"blender 将多策略信号合并。"
msgstr ""
"**Grupo**: Estrategias que comparten el mismo ``run_freq`` and "
"``run_timing`` belong to one Group; each Group can configure a ``blender`` "
"para fusionar múltiples señales de estrategia."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/1. overview.md:11
